description: Rare chance to own a SINGLE-FAMILY home in the heart of SOUTH BOSTON, where West meets East Broadway, offered with NEWLY ADDED GARAGE PARKING!! You are greeted by an expansive living area with soaring ceilings, a gas fireplace with separate reading nook, large dining area and open-concept kitchen with calacatta quartz countertops, complete with a guest powder room. Upstairs, two oversized bedrooms featuring ample closet space and abundant windows, separated by a full bathroom with a jet-tub/shower combo. Head outside to your beautifully landscaped, NEW PRIVATE PATIO of modern stone tiles and new wood fence, or relax on your private roof deck with city views! End your day in the finished basement, featuring a built-in bar and a TV den, ideal for movie nights. Additional perks include a new washer/dryer, hardwood floors throughout, newer tankless water heater & systems, additional storage. Walk to Southie’s hottest shops, bars, restaurants, coffee, grocery, and public transportation.
